/MENU
Run Program
Open frmMenu
 When btnExit clicked
  Close Program
 When btnDifficulty clicked
   Show frmDifficulty
   If btnMainMenu clicked
     Close frmDifficulty
     Open frmMenu
   If btnEasy clicked
      Difficulty = Easy
   If btnMedium clicked
      Difficulty = Medium
   If btnHard clicked
      Difficulty = Hard
 
 When btnColour clicked
  Show frmColour
   If btnMainMenu clicked
    Close frmColour
   If btnWhite clicked
    frmGameWhite used
   If btnBlue clicked  
    frmGameBlue used
   If btnGreen clicked
    frmGameGreen used
    
 When btnHighScore clicked
  Show frmHighScore
   If btnMainMenu clicked
    Close frmHighScore
  
 When btnControls clicked
  Show frmControls
